
Installing PyVXI11 1.11.3.5:
----------------------------

https://pypi.python.org/pypi/PyVXI11
$ sudo python setup.py install


Installing PyVISA 1.4:
----------------------

https://pypi.python.org/pypi/PyVISA/1.4
$ sudo python setup.py install


Installing NI-VISA 5.4:
-----------------------

http://joule.ni.com/nidu/cds/view/p/id/4234/lang/en
$ mkdir -p tmp/loop0; cd tmp
$ sudo mount -o loop,ro NI-VISA-5.4.0.iso loop0
$ tar xvzf loop0/nivisa-5.4.0f0.tar.gz
$ for x in rpms/*.rpm; do rpm2cpio < $x | cpio -id; done
$ sudo cp -r usr/local/vxipnp/. /usr/local/vxipnp
$ sudo umount tmp/loop0

